stimulus:
We need to check your headphones or speakers are working well enough for the experiment to run.

When you click continue you will hear a voice name a colour and you will be asked to identify the colour.
Great, that worked; just one more check!
Press continue to start the experiment! The word streams will start after you press continue
We will now ask you some additional questions.
In the last stream of words you hear any two-word phrases?

responses: {"Q0":"most of the phrases seemed to be pairs of words, an adjective and a noun, they were very toneless and repetitive"}
{"Q0":"Difficult without knowing the purpose of the experiment but the words would have been easier to listen to if spoken in a normal human voice, rather than one which sounded synthesised"}
